-- Chile's Lan Is in Talks to Buy Airbus A320s Worth $6.7 Billion, Echos Says
-- David Whitehouse
-- 2010-07-19T04:40:13Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-19/chile-s-lan-is-in-talks-to-buy-airbus-a320s-worth-6-7-billion-echos-says.html

          
          
             Lan Airlines SA of Chile is in talks
to buy between 50 and 70 Airbus A320s with a catalogue price of
between 3.7 billion euros and 5.2 billion euros, Les Echos
reported on its website, without saying where it got the
information.  
 Airbus declined to comment, the newspaper said.  
          
          


  


        